Pursuant to section 301 of D.C. Law 9-145, the &#8220;Omnibus Budget Support Act of 1992,&#8221; &#8220;the functions of the Office of Criminal Justice Plans and Analysis, established pursuant to section 4(a) of the Criminal Justice
        Supervisory Board Act of 1978 . . . and all positions, property, records, and unexpended balances of appropriations, allocations, and other funds available to or to made available relating the functions of the Office of Criminal Justice Plans
        and Analysis [were] transferred to the Mayor&#8217;s Office of Policy and Program Evaluation. . . .&#8221;
